import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"
import Navbar from "./components/Navbar"
import Feed from "./feed/Feed"

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <header>
        <Navbar />
      </header>
      <Switch>
        <Route path="/feed">
          <Feed />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/login"></Route>
        <Route path="/profile"></Route>
        <Route path="/"></Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
